{"tid":653441,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救］想問下有冇資料復原同notebook高手可以入一入黎","createTime":"2018-05-04T17:18:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T05:16:44.000Z","uid":90976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"05a65aa44b75ab2a8f4ec698df743d39a9e95360","tid":653441,"uid":90976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T17:18:05.000Z","msg":"首先，多謝左大大你入黎先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咁既，我部電腦係asus既E403SA，今日部電腦個底板自己無啦啦燒左。但其實我用左一年多少少，冇諗過咁易壞 咁化學。<br />\n<br />\n我對部電腦冇哂希望架喇，不過就想要返入面既資料。想問下有冇人會識或者識人識整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日都叫做去左四間問，但間間都話修復唔到。因為係on board既 個儲存體。拎左去asus問個反應係整得=預左啲野冇哂。而家完全唔知可以點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果咁岩有高手在此，就打救下啦～拜託拜託<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e85bc7b6cedf0ef99fa6fd8a2473e34db8c9555","tid":653441,"uid":90976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T17:19:19.000Z","msg":"揭起左既圖一張<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/011903_7ca47a2beb570e0995715239c25d0149.jpg[/img\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F011903_7ca47a2beb570e0995715239c25d0149.jpg%5B%2Fimg&d=LiGpq4PHcy29c2DU02GkF%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=b37af57d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/011903_7ca47a2beb570e0995715239c25d0149.jpg[/img</a>"},{"pid":"8a50c087894de416f18949bb4dc2904e1e321135","tid":653441,"uid":90976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T17:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/012014_08dcf1a57cb44de539ce8fb1f123c36b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%